لِكَ زَيَّنَ لِكَثِيرٍۢ مِّنَ ٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ قَتْلَ أَوْلَٰدِهِمْ شُرَكَآؤُهُمْ لِيُرْدُوهُمْ وَلِيَلْبِسُوا۟ عَلَيْهِمْ دِينَهُمْ ۖ وَلَوْ شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ مَا فَعَلُوهُ ۖ فَذَرْهُمْ وَمَا يَفْتَرُونَ","translation":"And, likewise, their belief in beings or powers that are supposed to have a share in God's divinity makes [even] the slaying of their children seem goodly to many of those who ascribe divinity to aught beside God, thus bringing them to ruin and confusing them in their faith. Yet, unless God had so willed, they would not be doing all this: stand, therefore, aloof from them and all their false imagery!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/926.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":78738,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78739,"position":2,"arabic":"زَيَّنَ","translation":"শোভন করা করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78740,"position":3,"arabic":"لِكَثِيرٍۢ","translation":"জন্যে অনেকের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78741,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78742,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ","translation":"মুশরিকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78743,"position":6,"arabic":"قَتْلَ","translation":"হত্যা করাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78744,"position":7,"arabic":"أَوْلَـٰدِهِمْ","translation":"সন্তানদের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78745,"position":8,"arabic":"شُرَكَآؤُهُمْ","translation":"শরিকরা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78746,"position":9,"arabic":"لِيُرْدُوهُمْ","translation":"যেন তারা ধ্বংস করে তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_137_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78747,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلِيَلْبِسُوا۟","translation":"এবং যেন তারা দুর